quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  16,30,"Ne balia abaritsanga Nyasaye nibareebwa mbu: “ nishina shia Nyasaye yeshia?” nibaboola mbu: “amalayi” ne balia bakhola obulayi khushialo khuno balinyoola amalayi, ne inzu yomwikulu ni indayi po ,ne inzu ya balia baria Nyasaye ni indayi muno"
  16,31,"Mumikunda chilawa tawe nichiabalinjilamwo, chiburanga hakari wachio emialo, balinyoolamwo eshiabenya. Endio nilwa Nyasaye arunganga abamuriitsanga"
  16,32,"Balia aba Malaika babafwisinjia nibakholele obulayi, balibaboolela mbu: “ omulembe kube ninanyu. Injile mwikulu khulwokhubeela kalia akamwakholanga.”"
  16,33,Ne libulao liabalindanga halali Abamalaika babetsele nohomba likhuwa lia Nyasaye wuwo liboolele? Ne endio nilwabakhola balia bali imbeli wabu. Ne Nyasaye shiyabakholela obubii tawe halali abeene nibo bekholela obubii
  16,34,"Mana nabatila khububii bwabakholanga mana\tnikababotokhana\tkalia akabatseshelanga"
  16,35,"Ne Abatsokaasi baboola mbu: “ Nyasaye achamanga shikhwakhalamile shiosi shiosi habundu wuwe tawe, efwe halala nohomba Abapapa befu, ne shikhwakhakanilekhwo shiosi shiosi tawe halali ye (akane)” kho mana endi nilwabakhola balia abali imbeli wabu. Kho shikali khubarumwa halali okhusia butswa oburume mubulafu"
  16,36,"Ne toto khwaruma Omurumwa mubuli omukanda ababoolele mbu: “mulaame Nyasaye ne mube ehale nende shetani” mubo balimwo ba Nyasaye yalunjisia, ne mubo balimwo bobukori bwakhoyeshela. Kho muchende khushialo mana mulolekhwo indukho yabayingasi shingala yali.”"
  16,37,"Kata noli nende okhwenya muno mbu balunjikhe, (manya mbu) Nyasaye shalunjisinjia ulia owatila okhukora tawe. Ne shibalinyoola ubahabina tawe"
  16,38,"Nabo betsubanga khulira lia Nyasaye eshitsubo shia amani mbu: “Nyasaye shalilamusia abafwa tawe.” Khulwa shina ? ni indakano eyalachilwa khuye, halali Abandu abanji shibamanyile tawe"
  16,39,"Kho abenoosilie kalia akabakabukhanila, ne mbu kho Abakhayi bamanye mbu bo toto ni ababeeyi"
  16,40,"Likhuwa liefu khushindu shia khwenya khuboolanga butswa mbu: “ba’’ nishiba"
  16,41,"Ne balia bawuya shichila Nyasaye nibamalile okhukholelwa obubii, toto khwitsa okhubetsusilia khushialo obulayi, ne omurungo kwomwikulu ni omukhongo muno, bamanyangakhwo bayie"
  16,42,Balia abefwila mana nibesikanga butswa Nyasaye wabu omulesi
  16,43,Nafu shikhwaruma imbeli wuwo halali Abasatsa abakhwafimbulilanga obufimbuli. Mana mureebe abali nobwitsulili nikali mbu shimumanyile tawe
  16,44,"Khubimanyisio bili habulafu nende mubitabu. Ne khweshia amachelo kho winoosilie Abandu akeshibwa khubo , khobanyoole okhupaara"
  16,45,Ne koo basuubilanga mbu bali nomulembe balia abakholanga ebifwanga mbu Nyasaye shiyetsa okhubayibisia muliloba tawe nohomba shalabarerera eshinyasio nabo nibalamanyile tawe
  16,46,"Nohomba shalabatila khutsinjendo tsiabu eyi nande eyi, Mana shibalanyala okhupwotsokha tawe"
  16,47,Nohomba mbu shalabahelesia eshinyasio shiokhurisia khulwa okhututuyilia shititi shititi? Toto Nyasaye wuwo ni omuholo oweshisa muno
  16,48,"Koo! Shibalolangakhwo buli bia Nyasaye yaloonga eshinikha shiabio shibotokhonanga okhurula omukhono omulunji nende omukaata ne binamilanga Nyasaye, nabio nibihotselesiye"
  16,49,"Ne binamilanga Nyasaye biosi bichendanga mwikulu nende khushialo , mutsisolo nende Abamalaika boosi, ne shibelolanga tawe"
  16,50,"Baritsanga Nyasaye wabu owuli hekulu wabu, ne bakholanga eliabalomesibungwa"